{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01LytqLcLuTcy2JJGV1uARqg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. The 3-node Elasticsearch cluster is deployed and fully functional.\n\n## Result\n\n**Cluster status: `green`, 3 nodes, all Ready.** Reads and writes succeed over HTTPS through the `es-http` Service.\n\n### What was deployed (native K8s only — no operators/CRDs)\n- **ConfigMap `es-config`** — `elasticsearch.yml` with security + TLS enabled.\n- **Service `es-transport`** (headless) — node discovery on 9300.\n- **Service `es-http`** (ClusterIP) — HTTPS on 9200, the required entry point.\n- **PodDisruptionBudget `es-pdb`** — `minAvailable: 2`.\n- **StatefulSet `es`** — 3 replicas, image `docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:8.11.1`, 2Gi PVC each.\n\n### Key configuration decisions\n- **HTTP TLS** uses the existing `es-http-tls` secret. The cert SAN `*.elasticsearch.svc` covers `es-http.elasticsearch.svc`, so HTTPS hostname verification works.\n- **Transport TLS** set to `verification_mode: certificate` (CA-chain only), since the wildcard SAN doesn't cover per-pod transport DNS names.\n- `ELASTIC_PASSWORD` sourced from the `elastic-password` secret for bootstrap.\n\n### One issue hit and fixed\nThe first apply deadlocked: a default StatefulSet uses `OrderedReady`, so only `es-0` started — but it couldn't bootstrap alone because `cluster.initial_master_nodes` requires es-0/1/2, and the others never launched (`master not discovered yet`). Fixed by adding **`podManagementPolicy: Parallel`** so all three pods start together and form the cluster. (This field is immutable, so the StatefulSet + PVCs were recreated.)\n\n### Verification (run from the in-cluster `curl-test` pod against `https://es-http:9200`)\n- Health: `cluster_name: es-cluster`, `status: green`, `number_of_nodes: 3`\n- Write: `PUT /karma-test/_doc/1` → `\"result\":\"created\"`\n- Read: `GET /karma-test/_doc/1` → `\"found\":true`\n\nThe manifest is saved at `stage_01/es.yaml`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":448,"cache_creation_input_tokens":978,"cache_read_input_tokens":45467,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":978},"output_tokens":5,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"983f1067-3d89-4893-a9cd-2e2e3ac52fdf","uuid":"edce6ed1-48aa-49c7-bf2d-f61e99a5b141","request_id":"req_011CcAhrUDsYtsY79kpFm1sc"}
